result.name: 生記山西刀削麵

reviews.text:
The Daoxiao noodles have a firm texture that’s resistant to the bite, while cooked through to the perfect extent.  I ordered fermented beef tripe as topping, while the restaurant offers a wide range of choices including not just the common toppings in local restaurant like pork chop, chicken wings and such, but also various Sichuan styled topping. 
Also I love the earthy taste of the milk tea contained in the iron cup.

I ordered Lanzhou beef noodles, spiciest level, and it was really spicy! Normally it doesn’t happened in Hong Kong. Soup is good, the beef is good, but the noodles could be better. Maybe I would try different noodles next time. Overall, I like it, and wouldn’t mind to come back here again.
Delicious food at good value.  Best noodles in yuen long.
Super Delicious Shan Xi style knife sliced noodles, hot and spicy. Special dishes and dinner set too.
Nice food with spicy taste.
